    <string name="custom_description">Custom plant description</string>
    <string name="monstera_description">Monstera (Monstera deliciosa) is a popular tropical houseplant known for its large, glossy, heart-shaped leaves with unique holes and splits. It thrives in bright, indirect light and is low-maintenance.</string>
    <string name="orchid_description">Orchids (Phalaenopsis) are elegant tropical plants known for their stunning, long-lasting flowers. They thrive in bright, indirect light and require careful watering and humidity.</string>
    <string name="zz_plant_description">The ZZ plant (Zamioculcas zamiifolia) is a hardy, low-maintenance indoor plant known for its glossy, dark green leaves.</string>
    <string name="snake_plant_description">The Snake Plant is a resilient and low-maintenance plant with tall, sword-like leaves featuring green and yellow variegation.</string>
    <string name="spider_plant_description">The Spider Plant is a hardy and adaptable houseplant with long, arching, variegated leaves.</string>
    <string name="aloe_vera_description">Aloe Vera is a versatile succulent with thick, fleshy leaves filled with gel known for its medicinal and skincare benefits.</string>
    <string name="african_violet_description">The African Violet is a compact houseplant with fuzzy leaves and vibrant flowers in purple, pink, or white.</string>

